snippet.title: FIEFDOM | Discord Teaser
snippet.description:
FIEFDOM is an exciting singleplayer and multiplayer melee-slasher set in a unique, playerbase-driven universe. Developed by a passionate team of over 20 professionals from around the world, FIEFDOM aims to redefine the slasher genre by pushing the boundaries of what's possible in action combat games and narrative storytelling.

Don't forget to join our Discord community!
https://discord.gg/nufpxHrjrS

Follow FIEFDOM on our socials!
• Facebook https://www.facebook.com/WhiteTowerGames
• Twitter https://twitter.com/fiefdomthegame
• Tiktok https://tiktok.com/@playfiefdom
• Reddit https://www.reddit.com/r/fiefdom/

Visit our Website!
https://playfiefdom.com/
